    {"name": "Asana", "id": "command-group:asana", "action_count": 14, "file": "asana", "description": "This package enables robust integration with Asana via the Asana v2 API. It delivers comprehensive CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for Tasks, Projects, and Comments (Stories) on both Tasks and Projects. This package is ideal for automating workflows, project management, and collaboration tasks within Asana from Automation Anywhere bots. 주요 액션: Connect(Connects to Asana using an API token or...)、Create comment on task(Creates a comment on a specified Asana t...)、Create project(Creates a new project in Asana with the...)、Create task(Creates a new task in an Asana workspace...)、Delete comment(Deletes a specific comment from an Asana...) 외 9개."},
